or fremtidig campus sammen med H\u00f8gskolen i S\u00f8r-Tr\u00f8ndelag. H\u00f8yskolen blir fusjonert med NTNU fra \u00e5rsskiftet."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "student"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "4949ba76e5c2998eb0c7f2882d2fd43b93d5c3b5a43526f486dadb50d9bcb9f3"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-08-11T10:35:07.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "De samfunnsmessige gevinstene ved \u00e5 samle NTNU er st\u00f8rre enn kostnadene, sier rapport."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/meninger/kronikker/article10660223.ece/4t9fjl/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Hovedbygning_5716.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/9864d531fb393e0590c509364bc03d094df29575.jpg?598d6b72"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Anbefaler NTNU-samling -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "9864d531fb393e0590c509364bc03d094df29575"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim", "ukeadressa", "eadressa", "skattelister", "d\u00f8dsfall", "tr\u00f8nder", "trafikk"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "nyheter,trondheim,ukeadressa,eadressa,skattelister,d\u00f8dsfall,tr\u00f8nder,trafikk"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "student"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": "samle"}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["kunnskapsdepartementet", "m\u00f8reforskning", "hist", "h\u00f8gskolen", "gl\u00f8shaugen", "dragvoll", "isaksens"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "s\u00f8r-tr\u00f8ndelag"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "torbj\u00f8rn r\u00f8e isaksen"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "student"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/meninger/kronikker/article10660223.ece/4t9fjl/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Hovedbygning_5716.jpg"}, {"field": "og-